{
  "chapter": 148,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙在两名美婢引路下抵达醉风楼，与管中邪、昌平君、昌文君饮宴。管中邪借罚酒试探项少龙腿伤，项少龙虽警觉却未露破绽。他点归燕陪酒，又在众人推荐下召来咸阳最红名妓单美美。单美美色艺双绝，舞姿动人，项少龙识破她乃嫪毐姘头、被管中邪和莫傲利用来暗害自己的工具。单美美为项少龙斟酒时趁广袖遮掩下毒，项少龙看在眼中，内心挣扎是否当场揭破毒酒玄虚。本章展现了青楼声色场景下暗藏的杀机，项少龙在敌人的美人计中保持清醒。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项大人迟来，虽是情有可原，却仍须先罚三杯酒，好使酒意上能大家看齐，否则喝下去定斗项大人不过。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 148,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "text": "管大人的话像你的剑般令项某人感到难以抵挡，哪敢不从命。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 148,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_yang_yu",
      "text": "姑娘怎么称呼？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 148,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_ping_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌平君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这真是咸阳城的奇闻，原来少龙竟是花丛里的高手。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 148,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌文君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "少龙自是高手，否则怎把纪才女收归私有，大兄说的应是青楼的老手才对。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 148,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "杨豫",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "奴家叫杨豫，项大人莫要忘记。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 148,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "且慢，在喝第二杯酒前，请项大人先点菜。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 148,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是点好了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 148,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌文君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "点的是陪酒唱歌的美人儿，只限两个，免致明天爬不下榻到田猎场去。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 148,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "楼主已把最红的几位姑娘留下来暂不侍客，就是等项大人不致无美食可点。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 148,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_ping_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌平君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我们身边的人儿们少龙也可点来陪酒，见你是初来甫到，就让你一回吧！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 148,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_chang_ping_jun",
      "text": "我没有逼你让给我呀！勉强的事就勿做，今晚我只点归燕姑娘陪酒，因为头更钟响时，小弟便要回家交差。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 148,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项大人除非忍心仗剑杀人，否则今晚休想本楼的姑娘肯眼睁睁放你回家睡觉。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 148,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "杨豫",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "让奴家今晚为项大人侍寝好吗？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 148,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "非不愿也，是不能也，小弟腿伤未愈，实在有心无力，请各位仁兄仁姊体谅。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 148,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "是我们脑筋不灵光，应全体受罚酒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 148,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "杨豫",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "大人莫忘还要再来找奴家。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 148,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌文君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "有一个菜式少龙不能不点，否则我两兄弟和管大人都会失望，就是咸阳城无人未闻芳号的单美美姑娘。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 148,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我是身在咸阳耳在别处，为何我从未听过有这么一位美人儿？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 148,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "幸好单美美的耳朵不在这里，否则休想她肯来，可能以后听到项大人的大名，她都要掩着香耳报复。人来！给项大人请归燕和单美美两位美人来。今晚我是主人，自然该以最好的东西奉客。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 148,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_yan",
      "speaker_name": "归燕",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "大人恩宠，奴家先敬大人一杯！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 148,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌文君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这叫迷汤、酒汤双管齐下，少龙小心今晚出不了醉风楼，腿伤发作哩！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 148,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_yan",
      "speaker_name": "归燕",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "大人的腿受伤吗？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 148,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_yan",
      "speaker_name": "归燕",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "酒能镇痛，大人请喝酒。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 148,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌文君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "归燕这么乖，少龙理应赏她一个嘴儿。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 148,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_yan",
      "speaker_name": "归燕",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "大人真吝啬。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 148,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_yan",
      "speaker_name": "归燕",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "大人比狮虎还要粗壮哩！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 148,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "text": "欢迎单姑娘芳驾。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 148,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "单美美",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "单美美拜见项大人！",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 148,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_ping_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌平君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们的单美人是否见项大人而心动，变得这么含羞答答、欲语还休的引人样儿。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 148,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌文君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "项大人的腿伤是否立即好了？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 148,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "text": "英雄配美人，单美人还不先敬项大人一杯，以作见面礼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 148,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_yan",
      "speaker_name": "归燕",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "大人忘记奴家哩！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 148,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "单美美",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "美美先喝一半，余下的代表美美对大人的敬意，大人请赏脸。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 148,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    }
  ],
